                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.102 Ic/15: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ruddock</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-08-12T14:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 12, 1921—2 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>226. Your 283, August 9, 5 p.m.</p>
                <p>Denial of asylum should be left to diplomatic body and nationality concerned.
                    Report details of any case/actually arising.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
